data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. This beautiful home is in a quiet neighborhood called Sola Vista. It was built in 2020 and has 2,267 square feet of living space on a big 0.14-acre lot.    Inside, you'll find an open layout that makes the house feel spacious and bright. The kitchen is especially nice with fancy granite countertops, perfect for cooking and entertaining.    There are two master bedrooms, each with its own bathroom, which is great for a big family or if different generations live together.    The floors in the main areas are tiled, and the bedrooms have soft carpet. The ceilings are high, giving the home a grand feeling. There's also a useful drop station near the garage for storing things.    Outside, there's a big covered porch in the front and a large backyard for outdoor activities. In the Sola Vista neighborhood, there's a shared pool for residents to use.    This home is in a quiet cul-de-sac and is close to good schools, shopping areas, and restaurants. It's also not too far from the beach and Disney attractions, about a 45-minute drive.    You should schedule a showing to see this amazing home with its open layout, high ceilings, and lots of natural light. It's a dream home waiting for you!  If you use our preferred lender ( Oliver Khedawy ) you may be eligible for a $2500 lender credit . 100% financing available.
